CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 23, 1954, pg. 6 reads:"Accomplice - Landrew Smith, 25, of 6223 1/2 Station Street, was sentenced on Wednesday to five to ten years in penitentiary for participating in a robbery with Herman Blackman, 25, of 15 Perry Street, whom police say was responsible for the theft of thirteen Cadillacs between June and September. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Landrew Smith, wearing hat, seated left on bench awaiting sentencing in Allegheny County Courthouse
